
Ranger Help for: bringword
==========================

SYNTAX:      bringword on <player>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,sea,lake,river,road,
             beach,underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside,port
SLOT COST:   13
BASE SP:     60 sp
SKILL TYPE:  knowledge

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to call upon his friends of the wild to
go out and search for a target player and return with a report
of his or her whereabouts. You will never know exactly where the
target is relative to you other than if he or she is close to you,
on the continent, or not.

